author: Second Wind
description:
In this episode of Storycraft, Jess chats with actor, writer, and BAFTA-nominated video game developer Cyrus Nemati about how voice acting and character writing are synergistic skills.

Music used in order of appearance:
Hotel Krat - Lies of P OST
Greenpath - Hollow Knight OST
Night Market - Stardew Valley OST
The Great Archives - Sea of Stars OST
Queen's Gardens - Hollow Knight OST
The Lost Village of Docarri (Day) - Sea of Stars OST
Mines (Star Lumpy) - Stardew Valley OST
Storytime Interlude: Partida of Prophecy - Sea of Stars OST
North Coast 500 - Burnhouse Lane OST
